"""Test get_available_initiator_wwn_as_list."""
initiator = self.provisioning.get_available_initiator_wwn_as_list()
if initiator:
    self.assertIsInstance(initiator, list)
    self.assertIsNotNone(re.match(constants.WWN_SEARCH_PATTERN_16,
        initiator[0]))
else:
    self.skipTest(
        'test_get_available_initiator - Unable to get an available initiator.')
